    "The factor (1 -S †) has a simple interpretation: it picks out the interacting part of S and ensures that the result vanishes if the particles do not interact.",
    "Indeed, the product on the left manifestly vanishes in free theory by equations of motion.",
    "The above identity can be applied in any state.",
